PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of RUTH CAROL FELDMAN, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as a member of the National Capital Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Darlene Julianne Hincks, whose term has expired.
